{"tid":1504953,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［速遞］Pickuphero 討論","createTime":"2019-08-25T12:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T11:48:57.000Z","uid":67494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"146188efeedc6b905bbd66879114fc7b97c68c85","tid":1504953,"uid":67494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:17:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人做緊？<br />\n諗住partime做"},{"pid":"a370e7ed912f4b0c5279e98db8c1e14ad76567ec","tid":1504953,"uid":68935,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:16:56.000Z","msg":"呢間野之前叫pickup , 後來改左名叫pickupp，<a href=\"http://連domain都由com改埋.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%80%A3domain%E9%83%BD%E7%94%B1com%E6%94%B9%E5%9F%8B.io&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DuL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=ba260225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">連domain都由com改埋.io</a><br />\n究竟點解又改名又domain?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩年前公司試用過呢間公司送貨，呢個經驗我呢世都記得，真係好嬲，又俾老細屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我公司賣小型電子產品，有一次佢有個速遞員好夜先收貨，早上接左單，但夜晚7-8點收貨，我本身係揀左4小時送貨，唔準時唔緊要，起馬都有d交帶，打俾我通知遲d到都沒問題，好啦，我同個客講話當晚上遲d收貨有沒問題？個客話ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好啦我就通知個速遞員當晚送都沒問題，速遞員話ok, <br />\n<br />\n屌，點知個速遞員11點幾打黎話，可唔可以聽日先送，太夜，我心想屌，你又遲到又拎左貨又唔係即日送，我明明揀左4小時送，仆街運費貴幾十蚊，得d禁既服務，夜晚打去hotline 又沒人幫手，即係要我硬食啦，我又打去同個客講明天送好唔好，個客都噪噪地，屌左我幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我只能硬食，只能叫佢改另一日<br />\n<br />\n件事仲未完呀！屌！到聽日我打俾個速遞叫佢盡快送去，屌！打極俾個速遞員都搵唔到佢，手機又息左，搵佢唔到！我跟打去個hotline 問，佢地話都搵緊個速遞員！如果搵唔到叫我報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我心想，屌！個速遞係你公司，點解要我報警，最終要大後日先搵到個司機，件貨仲未送，同埋唔知點解件貨拆過，最後佢地公司話賠俾我！ 攪左成個禮拜！先有個經理級既人<br />\n<br />\n我呢世都唔會用呢間公司！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3024537ac21840df58e8f2650f56e43333bda215","tid":1504953,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196f4e77baff50246dce20ea5142a68c39806ffb","tid":1504953,"uid":186668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:08:54.000Z","msg":"返過<br />\n垃圾公司一間<br />\n錢又小 仲要扣2成手續費<br />\n有次試下接件接左張送返自己學校department 既單<br />\n拎完件先發現個收件係個大陸人TA 放緊假<br />\n算啦 反正預左放件野落我自己locker 等閒日再送<br />\n結論係錢小浪費時間"},{"pid":"f87a1d37b7733b9f2af26dfb1d19a60cdf4c657a","tid":1504953,"uid":67494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"返順phone車步兵好無"},{"pid":"56657bc594eba440638efd4fc7bbf4edf9ba745b","tid":1504953,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"呢排見佢係咁搵人做"},{"pid":"4016124184e1074a3d45b48df4080409baf55c4e","tid":1504953,"uid":67494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56657bc594eba440638efd4fc7bbf4edf9ba745b","tid":1504953,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"呢排見佢係咁搵人做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"我報左名"},{"pid":"8c6b938d2eb8393a94f1b24d14233fdd9ad7814a","tid":1504953,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4016124184e1074a3d45b48df4080409baf55c4e","tid":1504953,"uid":67494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56657bc594eba440638efd4fc7bbf4edf9ba745b","tid":1504953,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"呢排見佢係咁搵人做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"我報左名"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:28:59.000Z","msg":"個人覺得真係得閒無野做先好開機做"},{"pid":"7446f301904faf356c2666a056d9af888ba21a1a","tid":1504953,"uid":67494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c6b938d2eb8393a94f1b24d14233fdd9ad7814a","tid":1504953,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4016124184e1074a3d45b48df4080409baf55c4e","t